Titolo: Ghostbusters (2016 video game)

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Ghostbusters is a twin stick shooter video game developed by FireForge Games and published by Activision for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One. Taking place after the events of the 2016 film, the game features four-player cooperative gameplay where players control new Ghostbusters characters to defeat enemy ghosts. The game had a development cycle of 8 months, and was released in July 2016. The game was panned by critics, and considered one of the worst video games of 2016.

Genere: Shoot \'em up / Twin Stick Shooter 

Valutazione: N/A
